{
  "stem": "9898.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was so thankful, when he was doing this, he said to me in German-- but I'll say it in English-- Herr Doctor-- he even gave me the title-- I will make you a small and pretty K-L.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He did me a great a favor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It's-- these are moments which are unforgettable, you know, in somebody's life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, in Mielec, at a certain time when there was a concentration camp, the work stopped because the Russians were approaching.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they closed the factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they closed the camp and sent everyone out to Wieliczka.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This is a small village in Poland, where they were, for hundreds of years, salt mines-- and deep, thousands of miles down.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I went down there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had a factory-- Heinkel factory in planes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were producing planes there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But it was really something-- but there were so many of us, they didn't need us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they sent a big group to Flossenburg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Flossenburg was a camp in southern Germany, in south Germany-- a killer camp, 35,000 to 40,000 people there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, when I came there, we were working in the stone quarries, cutting stones and carrying them from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Two-- I was working with another guy from here to there, and from there back to here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That's a whole day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And one soldier, SS soldier with sub-machine gun, screaming, schnell!",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Fast, fast, faster!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the ration was food, so we're getting around 250 calories a day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So every three, four, four weeks, five weeks maximum, they had to change-- the, the new transports were coming in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I felt I that I'm dying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And one day I was standing and working there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
